d, or unexpected bump could spell capture… and an uncertain fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526310/extras/37b1078ba0d6d07de6294d7b1c2bf321.poster.avif?t=1773392880\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526310/extras/37b1078ba0d6d07de6294d7b1c2bf321.webm?t=1773392880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526310/extras/37b1078ba0d6d07de6294d7b1c2bf321.mp4?t=1773392880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
